headline: YMCA of the USA Deepens Collaboration with DaVita to Drive Kidney Health Initiatives in Seven Communities
summary: CHICAGO and DENVER, Feb. 27, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- YMCA of the USA (Y-USA), the national resource office for the 2,600+ YMCAs across the country, is excited to expand its collaboration with DaVita, a leading provider of comprehensive kidney care, to advance chronic disease education and prevention for individuals and their families who are either managing or at risk for chronic kidney disease (CKD). CKD disproportionately affects individuals with risk factors such as hypertension and diabetes
